    dwc:basisOfRecord <http://treatment.plazi.org/id/EE5187839E6AFF90FF4EF8BDFAB2FABB/GJ2021070101>, <http://treatment.plazi.org/id/EE5187839E6AFF90FF4EF8BDFAB2FABB/YUNGL20220120> ;
